item.title: CVE-2019-5633|2024-09-16T16:42:37.789Z -- belwith%20products%2C%20llc -- hickory%20smart
item.description: An insecure storage of sensitive information vulnerability is present in Hickory Smart for iOS mobile devices from Belwith Products, LLC. The application's database was found to contain information that could be used to control the lock devices remotely. This issue affects Hickory Smart for iOS, version 01.01.07 and prior versions.

item.title: CVE-2019-5632|2024-09-16T21:57:21.046Z -- belwith%20products%2C%20llc -- hickory%20smart

This issue affects Hickory Smart for Android, version 01.01.43 and prior versions.
